(a) Calculation of wavenumber ($ ar{
u}$): $\lambda = 5800 	ext{ Å} = 5800 	imes 10^{-8} 	ext{ cm} = 5800 	imes 10^{-10} 	ext{ m}$. $ ar{
u} =  rac{1}{\lambda} =  rac{1}{5800 	imes 10^{-10} 	ext{ m}} = 1.724 	imes 10^6 	ext{ m}^{-1} = 1.724 	imes 10^4 	ext{ cm}^{-1}$. (b) Calculation of the frequency ($
u$): $
u =  rac{c}{\lambda} =  rac{3 	imes 10^8 	ext{ m s}^{-1}}{5800 	imes 10^{-10} 	ext{ m}} = 5.172 	imes 10^{14} 	ext{ s}^{-1}$.

